[SN]TITLE[SN]
Essentra in Newport takes on 70 new staff at its packaging firm

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Seventy jobs are being created in Newport with the expansion of a specialist packaging company.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Essentra, which set up a plant on the city's Imperial Park in 2014, will more than double its staff to over 100.
